summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Alonzo Avenue Northwest from the West 67th Street to West 70th Street et al in the City of Seattle, by laying watermains under Ordinance No. 24849, creating Local Improvement District No. 2389 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
